Cache Computation Result

Source: R/auto_tuning_helpers.R
cache_result.Rd

Stores computation result in cache for future use.

Usage

cache_result(cache, candidate, cut.off, mx, result)

Arguments

cache

Cache object.

candidate

Parameter candidate.

cut.off

Cut-off threshold.

mx

Mobility matrix.

result

Computation result.
